                    </div>
                    <span>A well writen documentary of an inspirational woman.  This book gives life to significant events taking place in the fight for civil rights.  In particular, reading about her Freedom Ride on a bus through the American South gave chilling reality to the ordeal.  Fannie Lou Hamer is a pivotal figure in American history.</span>
                  
              
